title: Z-RO Drankin.and.Driven [Caddi44]
description:
Z-Ro has been cranking out roughly an album per year for the past twenty years. Friday morning he delivered the 2016 contribution to his discography -- a new album called Drankin' & Drivin' which finds the Houston legend in rare form, snarling lines like  "If you was struggling back in '97 when I started this/ And yo' ass still struggling in 2016, your hustle is garbage, bitch."
